Standards-Version: 3.5.2

Package: megistos-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libmegistos1 (= ${Source-Version}), libc6-dev, typhoon-dev (>> 1.10.3), libncurses4-dev | libncurses5-dev | libncursesw5-dev
Description: Development files for Megistos BBS
 Megistos is a stable, multilingual, traditional BBS system written to
 resemble The Major BBS (R) from a user's point of view.
 .
 This is the C development toolkit for writing Megistos BBS applications
 (called modules) and for compiling the entire system.

Package: libmegistos1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, typhoon1 (>= 1.10.3)
Description: Shared library for all Megistos BBS software
 Megistos is a stable, multilingual, traditional BBS system written to
 resemble The Major BBS (R) from a user's point of view.
 .
 This is the shared library needed by all Megistos BBS components.

